WEBVTT

21:02.316 --> 21:03.983
And... about the case...

21:04.233 --> 21:05.983
We were completely
honest with them, right?

21:06.941 --> 21:07.941
That's all true.

21:08.941 --> 21:10.441
But it seems someone told them

21:10.441 --> 21:13.233
that the girl is undergoing
treatment for a mental illness.
